<h2 style="margin:0 0 8px; color:#2E2E38; font-size:22px;">Retire nan Sol</h2>
<p style="margin:0 0 16px; color:#5D6345; font-size:14px;">Ou retire nan Sol <strong><%= @circle.name %></strong> paske ou pa t kapab peye kontribisyon ou.</p>

<div style="background:#fef2f2; border:1px solid #fca5a5; border-radius:14px; padding:14px 16px; margin-bottom:14px;">
  <div style="font-size:14px; color:#991b1b; font-weight:700;">Penalite: -50 pwen kredi</div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#991b1b; margin-top:6px;">Nivo kredi ou desann. Ou ka rebati li lè ou patisipe nan lòt Sol epi peye a lè.</div>
</div>

<div style="background:#fcfcf9; border:1px solid #e8e3cf; border-radius:14px; padding:14px 16px; margin-bottom:14px;">
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#2E2E38;">Ou ka toujou kreye oswa rantre nan yon lòt Sol. Chak peman a lè ap ede ou remonte nivo ou.</div>
</div>

<p style="margin:0;">
  <a href="<%= sol_circles_url %>" style="color:#2E2E38; background:#C5A059; text-decoration:none; padding:10px 16px; border-radius:10px; font-weight:700; display:inline-block;">Wè Sol Yo</a>
</p>

<p style="margin:16px 0 0; color:#5D6345; font-size:13px;">Avèk respè,<br><strong>Zèllus</strong></p>
